        "timestamp": "2020-09-23 20:14:00.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1\n> \n> Version (pom.xml and version.properties) needs to be bumped as 1.4.0 is already released\n> \n> And if this change is intended for >Guilin, then may need to create \"guilin\" branch first\n\nActually, we were supposed to resolve these in Guilin - so I wanted to get this in under the wire, as long as you're okay with that (I was surprised that bumping spring version from 4 to 5 didn't break the compile, but it didnt ... whether it still works is a very different matter, of course)\n\n I'll bump the versions though - thanks!",
